<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Evernote FAQ</div><div><br /></div><div>How to create a local Notebook?</div><div>Click on “Option” (Alt) and then -&gt; File -&gt; New Local Notebook.</div><div>( It won’t show up if you just click on File ) </div></en-note>